  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nStatus of transaction sent on LTE with disabled mobile sync, and has already received confirmation on the network (can be checked on Etherscan), won't be updated immediately after confirmation in account view in tx history.\r\nTo update the status pull-to-refresh is needed.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nTx status is automatically updated immediately after confirmations are received on the network\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nTx status is not automatically updated\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Disable WiFi, have device on LTE\r\n- Disable using mobile data \r\n- Open Wallet\r\n- Send tx\r\n- Open tx history in account view\r\n- Check tx status on Etherscan (be sure to stay logged in)\r\n- After receiving confirmations and \"Success\" status on Etherscan check the status of the tx in tx history \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: Nightly 31/03\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\n[geth.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/6234815/geth.log)\r\n[Status.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/6234816/Status.log)\r\n",
